</span><span class='line'>&lt;title type="html"&gt;&lt;![CDATA[VMware 'Host SMBus controller not enabled!']]&gt;&lt;/title&gt;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;link href="http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2015/05/29/debug-kdump-vm/"/&gt;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;updated&gt;2015-05-29T14:21:00+08:00&lt;/updated&gt;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;id&gt;http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2015/05/29/debug-kdump-vm&lt;/id&gt;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;content type="html"&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.centos.bz/faq/111/"&gt;https://www.centos.bz/faq/111/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu/CentOS guest instances in VMware sometimes come up with the boot error message:
</span><span class='line'>&lt;code&gt;
</span><span class='line'>piix4_smbus 0000:00:007.3: Host SMBus controller not enabled!
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;This error is being caused because VMware doesn’t actually provide that level interface for CPU access, but Ubuntu try to load the kernel module anyway.&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;How to fix it: &lt;br/&gt;
</span><span class='line'>在虚拟机中
</span><span class='line'>&lt;code&gt;
</span><span class='line'>sudo vim /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist.conf
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code&gt;
</span><span class='line'>add the line:
</span><span class='line'>&lt;code&gt;
</span><span class='line'>blacklist i2c-piix4
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;reboot&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;hr /&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;似乎这个错误在centos6 + 3.10* 的内核，有时kdump不起作用。&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>]]&gt;&lt;/content&gt;
</span><span class='line'>  &lt;/entry&gt;
